The '''''Dauntless''''' was a [[Cruiser/Legends|cruiser]] in the [[New Republic Defense Fleet/Legends|New Republic Defense Fleet]] and [[Galactic Alliance Defense Fleet|Galactic Alliance Navy]] during the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].<ref name="SbS" /><ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

==History==
After the [[Battle of Fondor]], [[Carrier/Legends|carrier]] forces were deployed to protect the New Republic's major [[Shipyard/Legends|shipyards]].<ref name="BalP">''[[The New Jedi Order: Balance Point]]''</ref> In the period after the [[Battle of Yag'Dhul (26 ABY)|Battle of Yag'Dhul]], the ''Dauntless'' formed an important part of the force defending the [[Bilbringi Shipyards]], commanded by [[General/Legends|General]] [[Muun (individual)|Muun]].<ref name="SbS" /> When the [[Senate Select Committee for Refugees]] asked for the temporary reassignment of a quarter of Muun's forces to protect a group of [[Vray]], the ''Dauntless'' was excluded from the request.<ref name="SbS" />

Later, the ''Dauntless'' was part of the Alliance forces that participated in the [[Defense of Mon Calamari (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Defense of Mon Calamari]].<ref name="TUF" /> It later served in the [[Battle of Yuuzhan'tar|recapture]] of [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], where it was probably part of the [[Fourth Fleet (Galactic Alliance)|Fourth Fleet]], providing fire support to the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] flagship ''[[Right to Rule]]'' alongside two [[MC80B Star Cruiser]]s.<ref name="TUF" />

